                  "value": "sidebar-fournisseur"
                }
              ],
              "content": "<div class=\"sfc-card\" id=\"sidebar-fournisseur\">\n  <h3>Fournisseur de service</h3>\n  <p class=\"sfc-subtitle\">Ministère de la Sécurité</p>\n  \n  <div class=\"sfc-row\">\n    <span class=\"sfc-ico\">📞</span>\n    <span><strong>Téléphone :</strong> (+228) 22 20 86 54</span>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"sfc-row\">\n    <span class=\"sfc-ico\">✉️</span>\n    <span><strong>Email :</strong> contact@securite.gouv.tg</span>\n  </div>\n  \n  \n  <div class=\"sfc-row\">\n    <span class=\"sfc-ico\">📍</span>\n    <span><strong>Adresse :</strong> <a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/W7TGaeLhprWTtx3e8\" target=\"_blank\">Rue de l'Entente, Souza Nétimé A côté de l'ancienne Primature, Lomé</a></span>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"sfc-row\">\n    <span class=\"sfc-ico\">🌐</span>\n    <span><strong>Site web :</strong> <a href=\"https://securite.gouv.tg/\" target=\"_blank\">https://securite.gouv.tg/</a></span>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"sfc-row\">\n    <span class=\"sfc-ico\">🕐</span>\n    <span><strong>Ouverture :</strong> Lundi – Vendredi, 07h30 – 17h30</span>\n  </div>\n  \n  <h3 class=\"sfc-stitle\">Statistiques</h3>\n  \n  <div class=\"sfc-boxes\">\n    <div class=\"sfc-box\">\n      <p class=\"sfc-lbl\">Délai moyen réel de traitement</p>\n      <p class=\"sfc-val\">45 <span style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:normal;\">Jours</span></p>\n      <p class=\"sfc-sub\">Base: 6 derniers mois</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"sfc-box\">\n      <p class=\"sfc-lbl\">Demandes de la journée</p>\n      <p class=\"sfc-val\">128</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <a href=\"/statistiques\" class=\"sfc-link\" id=\"stats-link\">\n    <span class=\"sfc-link-ico\">➜</span> \n    Voir les statistiques détaillées\n  </a>\n</div>",
              "key": "sidebarFournisseurStats",
